  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist and follow!</h1><p><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/972280/extras/20657d715b946f76b4889b9f0deb86ad.poster.avif?t=1649945114\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/972280/extras/20657d715b946f76b4889b9f0deb86ad.webm?t=1649945114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/972280/extras/20657d715b946f76b4889b9f0deb86ad.mp4?t=1649945114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>An automatic station deep in the space has sent an alarm signal and then the connection disrupted. Your spaceship set off there to carry out reconnaissance. But all of a sudden you encounter huge forces of an unknown enemy.  Now there’s no way back –you either defeat him or die.<br><br>This game is a vertical scroll-shooter with numerous enemies and a gradually increasing level of complexity.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game feature:</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>24 original levels<br></li><li>eight-bit music<br></li><li>12 bosses<br></li><li>an endless level mode with strong enemies</li></ul>",
